  "detailed_description": "<strong><i>Prop and seek</i></strong> is a hide and seek game which up to 32 players take turns to hide or seek. You can be a prop to hide or be a hunter to find all hidden props.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PLAY WITH MAXIMUM OF 32 PLAYERS!</strong></h2><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You can set maximum number of players in the custom mode, or make it public and have fun with players from anywhere in the world!</li></ul></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1131720/extras/cad728994239dc4d40a07a2e743e8e6e.poster.avif?t=1705503260\" width=620 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1131720/extras/cad728994239dc4d40a07a2e743e8e6e.webm?t=1705503260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1131720/extras/cad728994239dc4d40a07a2e743e8e6e.mp4?t=1705503260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>　<br>　<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CHOOSE VARIOUS CHARACTERS AND ALIASES!</strong></h2><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You can have rare characters and aliases by completing achievements, or you can also simply purchase characters from our shop!</li></ul></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1131720/extras/bbbb3ae0c5b451e1389e647a470848ac.poster.avif?t=1705503260\" width=614 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1131720/extras/bbbb3ae0c5b451e1389e647a470848ac.webm?t=1705503260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1131720/extras/bbbb3ae0c5b451e1389e647a470848ac.mp4?t=1705503260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>　<br>　<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>USE JETPACK AND HUNT 'EM DOWN FROM SKY!</strong></h2><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You can also use additional features like jetpack, rocket launcher, and grenade!</li></ul></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1131720/extras/28a2a78d44b92f69f604487b21fb1912.poster.avif?t=1705503260\" width=614 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1131720/extras/28a2a78d44b92f69f604487b21fb1912.webm?t=1705503260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1131720/extras/28a2a78d44b92f69f604487b21fb1912.mp4?t=1705503260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>　<br>　<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GLANCE THROUGH YOUR PROFILE AND KNOW YOUR STATS!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Everything will be shown in your profile, which makes it so easy to figure out your strength or weakness!</strong></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1131720/extras/86c45663fe7784b7c04b750e6105fe04.poster.avif?t=1705503260\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1131720/extras/86c45663fe7784b7c04b750e6105fe04.webm?t=1705503260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1131720/extras/86c45663fe7784b7c04b750e6105fe04.mp4?t=1705503260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>　<br>　<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PLAY VARIOUS GAME MODES AND BRING UP YOUR RANKING IN COMPETITIVE!</strong></h2><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play custom games with your friends, chill on quick, and be a pro-gamer in competitive! You can also check your ranking on Steam. The competitive score ranges from 0 to 5000!</li></ul></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1131720/extras/47438f9103f7a674990f2a29024b975e.poster.avif?t=1705503260\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1131720/extras/47438f9103f7a674990f2a29024b975e.webm?t=1705503260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1131720/extras/47438f9103f7a674990f2a29024b975e.mp4?t=1705503260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>　<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><i>PROP AND SEEK RANK SYSTEM</i></strong></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1131720/extras/c2270b333af2f016eb2b5de5764a2f64.avif?t=1705503260\" width=620 height=92 /></span>",
